397
00:18:07,110 --> 00:18:08,790
Your victim can only be me.

398
00:18:09,350 --> 00:18:09,920
Got it?

399
00:18:10,940 --> 00:18:13,820
♪We can be each other's light♪

400
00:18:14,620 --> 00:18:18,220
♪I love you♪

