503
00:22:19,750 --> 00:22:20,510
Wen Yifan.

504
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:24,550
What's wrong?

505
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:25,590
Did you meet someone?

506
00:22:26,200 --> 00:22:27,720
