516
00:23:05,780 --> 00:23:06,200
Hello.

517
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:06,730
Hello.

518
00:23:07,270 --> 00:23:08,550
I ordered a cake for you.

519
00:23:08,550 --> 00:23:10,920
