526
00:23:29,920 --> 00:23:30,680
And...

527
00:23:31,960 --> 00:23:32,920
happy birthday.

528
00:23:51,350 --> 00:23:53,200
Let's consider my birthday this year

529
00:23:53,350 --> 00:23:54,240
